<para style="p">A psalm of Asaph.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />God, foreign nations have come into your inheritance;</para>

<para style="q1">they have defiled your holy temple;</para>

<para style="q1">they have turned Jerusalem into a heap of ruins.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />They have given the dead bodies of your servants as food to the birds of the skies,</para>

<para style="q1">the bodies of your faithful people to the beasts of the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />They have shed their blood like water around Jerusalem,</para>

<para style="q1">and there was none to bury them.</para>
